Umubare w'abanduye Coronavirus (COVID-19) uzagenda wiyongera mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Afurika y'Ubukungu no mu Bwongereza, kuva ku itariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Iyo umuntu atekereje ku bantu bose banduye icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) bagaragaza ibimenyetso bimwe mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Afurika y'Ubukungu no mu Bwongereza, biremeza ko nubwo impamvu zituma icyorezo cya COVID-19 gitera mu bihugu bitandukanye, cyakwirakwira mu bihugu byose vuba.
Mu rwego rwo kwita ku mibereho y'u Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bukomeye bigomba kwitegura kwakira abarwayi benshi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi, cyane cyane mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bukomeye.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, abantu benshi bafashwe bafite indwara y'ubuhumekero itaramenyekana mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko iyi ndwara yavuye ku bwoko bushya bwa coronavirus ubu bwitwa Coronavirus yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ikomeye 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara zituruka kuri SARS-CoV-2 zizitwa icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ubuhamya buhamya ko 80% by'abanduye COVID-19 bafite uburwayi buciriritse, urugero nk'indwara yo guhumeka cyangwa guhumeka nabi, kandi abenshi muri bo bashobora gukira.
Mu bantu 14 ku ijana, COVID-19 iba iturutse ku ndwara ikomeye igomba gukorerwa ibitaro, naho mu bantu 6 ku ijana, indwara ikomeye igomba kwitabwaho cyane.
Umubare w'abapfa bavurirwa muri COVID-19 ni 4%.
Muri iki gikorwa, tuzasuzuma uko COVID-19 ikwirakwira mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu ka Burayi n'u Bwongereza, maze tugereranye n'ibyo mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Nanone, umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri Afurika/Afurika y'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza ugiye kugereranywa n'uw'u Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abantu banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Afurika y'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza
Nk'uko byagenze mu Bushinwa, COVID-19 yakwirakwiriye mu bindi bihugu kandi icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyakwirakwiriye mu bindi bihugu nk'uko cyagenze muri icyo gihugu.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 5 Werurwe 2020, ikiganiro cya Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri na bagenzi be, bagaragaje ko abantu ba mbere bo mu Burayi banduye COVID-19 bakurikije uko WHO ibivuga.
Mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Afurika y'Ubukungu, abantu batatu ba mbere banduye indwara z'indwara ya coronavirus bagaragaye mu Bufaransa ku wa 24 Mutarama 2020; ni abantu baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa, bagasubira mu Bufaransa.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, COVID-19 yari imaze kwandura mu bihugu 30 byo mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, kandi kuva ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza ubu, abantu 39,768 ni bo banduye COVID-19 ndetse abantu 1,727 ni bo bapfuye, ndetse no mu Butaliyani hari abantu 17.750 banduye ariko abantu 1.441 bapfuye.
Gushyiraho umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 bose
Mu kigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no kurwanya indwara (ECDC), imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 ku rwego rw'igihugu, igera ku mibare isanzwe gusa, urugero nk'ibiro by'ubuzima mpuzamahanga, inzego z'ubuzima ku rwego rw'isi n'imirenge ndetse na OMS, ishyirwa ku murongo buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu kumenya uko COVID-19 ikwirakwira mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Afurika y'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, agereranywa n'u Butaliyani.
Mu rwego rwo kureba umubare w'abanduye COVID-19, turareba iminsi 14 y'uburumbuke bw'abanduye COVID-19, bityo tukareba uko COVID-19 ikura, mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Afurika y'Ubukungu no mu Bwongereza, mu gihe cy'ukwezi kwa mbere kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Nanone twabonye umubare w'abarwayi bose ku isi ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani za mu gitondo, ugereranyije n'uw'u Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Afurika y'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza
Ibipimo by'iminsi 14 by'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Afurika y'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza bikurikirana urugero rw'icyorezo cya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igitekerezo cya 1).
Mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Afurika y'Ubukungu n'u Bwongereza, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatangiye kwiyongera hafi ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, nyuma kiza kugera ku rwego rwo hejuru cyane hafi ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Ibindi bisobanuro).
Ibi byavuye ku mibare y'abanduye muri Italiya, ariko mu bihugu byose by'u Burayi/Afurika y'Ubukungu, umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wariyongereye kimwe (Ibindi bitangazamakuru).
Umubare wa 2 ugaragaza umubare w'abantu bose banduye COVID-19, mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Afurika y'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani za mu gitondo, ibindi bihugu 15 byo mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bwa Burayi n'u Bwongereza byari bifite umubare w'abarwayi nk'uwa Italiya, mu byumweru bitatu gusa mbere yaho.
Ibisubizo byacu bizagaragaza ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 uzamuka cyane mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Afurika y'Ubukungu no mu Bwongereza.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu bose banduye COVID-19 bugaragaza ko icyorezo cyugarije ibindi bihugu mu buryo bumwe.
Ibyo ni ko bimeze no mu bihugu bifite intego zitandukanye, abaganga ntibafasha abantu kimwe, ndetse wenda n'amategeko n'amategeko atandukanye agena abarwayi bagomba gukora ibizamini byo kumenya niba bafite COVID-19, ndetse no gukora ibizamini nyuma.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu bihugu by'u Butaliyani bari mu duce tw'icyorezo, bavuze ko abagera kuri 10% by'abarwaye COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, naho itangazamakuru rivuga ko ibitaro byo muri ibyo bihugu by'icyorezo byataye umutwe.
Raporo y'abantu banduye COVID-19 bajyanywe mu bitaro no/cyangwa mu bitaro bikuru ubu iri mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Afurika y'Ubukungu ku kigero cya 6% na 1% gusa (amakuru ntagaragara).
Ariko kandi, bagombye kubishyira hamwe neza kugira ngo bihuze n'amakuru agezweho avuga cyane ku ndwara n'urupfu.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-11 bwagaragaje ko mu Burayi habayeho ihinduka rikomeye mu by'ubuvuzi bukomeye n'uburiri buciriritse, aho habaye 29,2 mu Budage n'ibitanda 4,2 ku bantu 100.000 muri Porutugali.
Ibi byumvikanisha ko ibihugu bishobora kuba bifite ubushobozi bwo kwivuza kurusha u Butaliyani (12,5 mu bitaro bikuru byita ku barwayi n'ibitanda by'ibanze ku bantu 100.000 mu 201011).
Guteza imbere ubuvuzi bw'abarwayi birenze ibipimo by'ubuvuzi, kuko umubare w'abarwayi bo mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu k'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza ku bantu bavurirwa muri COVID-19 hamwe n'ibipimo by'ibyago byo kubura ibitanda mu bitaro bikuru, 90% byatanzwe mu makuru mashya ya gatandatu ya ECDC agenga icyihutirwa cy'ubukungu bwa COVID-19.
Kubera ko umubare w'abarwayi ukwirakwira cyane mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'u Burayi/Afurika y'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, ndetse n'ibitaro byo mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bukomeye bikunze gukoreshwa mu kubungabunga abaturage bo mu karere runaka, amakuru y'indwara n'ibitanda byo mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bukomeye agomba kuboneka ku buntu mu cyiciro cyiswe Nomenclature y'ibice by'amakuru cy'umwanya wa 2 (NUTS-2).
Ibihugu by'u Butaliyani n'ibindi bihugu biri hafi kubikora, bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyakwirakwiriye mu bihugu by'u Burayi/Afurika y'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bakomeye bigomba kwitegura uko byafata SARS-CoV-2 n'umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 bagasaba ubufasha, cyane cyane mu bitaro bikomeye, nk'uko bizakorwa mu bice by'icyaro by'u Butaliyani birimo iyi ndwara.
Nkuko byagaragajwe mu isuzuma ry'imimerere y'impanuka riherutse gukorwa na ECDC, uburyo bwihuse, bwiza kandi bwemewe ni ngombwa kugira ngo SARS-COV-2 itagenda ikwirakwira, ikurweho n'abantu banduye ikongera kugabanya ibiciro by'indwara ya contamintaion; kuko kumenya mbere y'igihe umubare w'abarwaye nta cyo bifasha abantu gufata imyanzuro kandi ibitaro ntibizaba bifite igihe cyo kubisobanukirwa, kubyemera no kubitegura mu gihe badabanje kugeragezwa.
Nanone kandi, ubushakashatsi bw'imimerere y'impanuka buvuga ko hari uburyo bwinshi bwo kugabanya ubwandu bw'indwara.
Hari amahirwe make mu gihe ibihugu bifite amahirwe yo kongera ingufu mu kurwanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 no gushyiraho ingufu mu buvuzi.
Iyo ibyo bitakozwe, inzego z'ubuzima zo mu bindi bihugu by'u Burayi/Afurika y'u Burayi zizajya zisaba abantu benshi kurushaho kurwara, bityo bakaba bakeneye kwitabwaho mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 (SARS-CoV-2), kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3000 kandi kigahitana abantu barenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, bigatuma kiba icyorezo gikomeye ku bantu.
Ku birebana n'umuti wa SARS-CoV, warwaye abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi mu mwaka wa 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba yaraturutse ku mbese kandi ifite ibimenyetso bimwe kandi ikagira ingaruka zimwe.
Nubwo COVID-19 idakomeye cyane kandi ntiyica abantu benshi nka SARS, ikwirakwira cyane kandi igakomeretsa abantu bakuru kurusha abakiri bato kandi igakomeretsa abagabo kurusha abagore.
Kubera ko ibitabo by'ubuvuzi bizakomeza kwandikwa, intego y'iyi ngingo ni iyo gutanga amakuru y'igihe gikwiriye no gusobanura ubushakashatsi buzakorwa kuri iyo ngingo.
Muri iki gice, tuzasuzuma ibintu by'ingenzi birebana n'indwara z'ibyorezo, imiterere y'umubiri, ubwandu bw'indwara, uburyo bwo kubimenya, uburyo bwo kuvurwa, ibipimo by'igihe umuntu azahura na zo n'uburyo bwo kwirinda indwara.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bitaraba, twiringiye ko iki gice kizagufasha kumenya icyo wakora kugira ngo urwanye iyo ndwara.
Umunsi mukuru wo mu gicucu wo ku itariki ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye umunsi udasanzwe kandi uzwi cyane mu Bushinwa, kuko babujijwe gusohoka mu minsi mikuru yose no mu byumweru byinshi bikurikiyeho kubera icyorezo gishya gikomeye.
Iyi virusi ihuriye cyane na coronavirus (CoV) yari indwara yo mu mutwe (SARS) mu mwaka wa 2003; ikaba yiswe SARS-CoV-2 na OMS ku wa 11 Gashyantare 2020, naho icyorezo cyayo cyiswe COVID-19 (COVID-19).
Iyo ndwara yaturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, ikwira mu Bushinwa hose no mu bihugu hafi 50 byo hirya no hino ku isi.
Ku itariki ya 2 Werurwe 2020, iyi virusi yatumye abantu barenga 80,000 barwara COVID-19, abantu barenga 40,000 barakira kandi bava mu bitaro ariko abantu barenga 3,000 barapfa.
OMS iragabisha ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi wa mbere w'abantu" kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Dukurikije PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, abagore basohoye ingingo zisaga 200 zivuga kuri COVID-19 harimo virusi, icyorezo, imiterere y'ubuzima, uburyo bwo kubimenya, n'uburyo bwo kubigeraho, kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku itariki ya 7 Mutarama 2020 isobanura uko virusi ikwirakwira mu bantu benshi.
Iki gice kigomba kugerageza gusobanura muri make ubushakashatsi buzakorwa kuri icyo kintu gishya kizakwirakwira mu buryo bwihuse.
Mu gihe bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS hamwe n'indi ndwara iterwa na CoV, indwara yo mu mutwe yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS, yasohotse mu mwaka wa 2012).
Nanone turi busuzume ibyo tumaze kumenya ku birebana n'uko twarwanya iyo ndwara, uko yahanwa n'uko ishobora kubaho, n'ibindi bibazo by'ingenzi.
Bivugwa ko COVID atari indwara y'ubwonko, kuko ahanini ituma 15% by'abantu bahura n'indwara y'ibicurane.
Ariko muri iki gihe, dufite virusi ya CoV igera kuri ebyiri, urugero nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatangiye icyorezo cy'indwara ya SARS-CoVs cyaturutse mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, kandi zikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu vuba, zigatuma abantu benshi bahitana abandi.
Niyo mpamvu COVID-19 iriho ubu ari cyo cyorezo cya gatatu cya COVID-19 cyigarije isi.
Nkuko bigaragara mu mibare: Icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero cy'umurongo wa 1,1, kitari cyamenyekanye, cyatangajwe bwa mbere i Wuhan ku wa 31 Gashyantare 2019 n'ikigo cy'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa.
Hashize iminsi irindwi, hashyizweho uburyo bwo gutangiza CoV.
