Ku munsi wa 20, abaganga batangaje ko indwara y'indwara y'ubwonko yanduye, ibyo bikaba byumvikanisha ko umuntu ashobora kuyikwirakwiza.
Ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, umugi wa Wuhan warafashwe, kandi imodoka zitwara abantu bose ntizongera gukora.
Ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama, ubwo ubushakashatsi bwatangiraga, mu bantu 41 barwaye iyo ndwara, 21 gusa ni bo bageze ku isoko ry'amafi ryo mu nyanja rya Wuhan aho indwara yatangiriye ku nyamaswa zitazwi.
Ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iyi ndwara ari icyorezo cy'icyorezo ku isi hose.
Kugeza ubu, iyi ndwara imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa hose no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 byo hirya no hino ku isi (Ibaruwa ya 2.2).
Kubera ko ibintu bizahinduka mu buryo bwihuse, ntibiramenyekana uko bizagenda mu rugero rwagutse cyangwa uko bizagenda mu rugero rwagutse.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 8.866 barimo n'abantu 4.021 bari bafite COVID-19 yabonetse amakuru mashya ku ndwara y'ubwandu iri hasi (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
