Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko ingurube z'ibishwi zishobora kugenda metero 15 cyangwa metero 8.2.
Hari abavuga ko virusi ishobora no gukwirakwira mu mazi mato y'umubiri aguma mu mwuka amasaha menshi, akorwa mu gihe umuntu avuze. Mu mazi y'umwuka no mu gihe umuntu ahumeka, kandi agenda, nta virusi iri mu mwuka.
