Gukurikirana abantu bahuye n'abarwayi, kwirinda ingendo, gukora ibizamini no gushyira abantu mu kato, Coronavirus 2020 muri Singapuru yagwiriye neza kurusha mu bindi bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, ariko nta bihano bikomeye nk'ifunga ry'ama resitora n'ibigo by'ubucuruzi.
Imirimo myinshi yabereye mu rugo, kandi muri Singapuru hatangiye itegeko ryo kuguma mu rugo ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe, ariko amashuri yatangiye gufungura mu gihe cy'umunsi mukuru wo ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe.
Hari n'ibindi bihugu byinshi byashyizeho imihati kugira ngo birwanye iyi ndwara, bigakoresha ingamba zo kugabanya umubare w'abarwayi, bihagarika ingendo, bigakora ibizamini, kandi bigashyira abantu mu kato, ariko hari n'ibindi bihugu bifite ingamba zo kugabanya ingamba zo kugabanya ingamba zo kugabanya ubwandu, urugero nka Islande na Koreya y'Epfo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ibiro by'amakuru bwagaragaje ko ibihugu byakoraga ubushakashatsi bwinshi, mu gihe byabaga bifite umubare muto w'abapfuye, bishobora kuba byaratumye abantu baba bafite ibimenyetso by'uburwayi cyangwa batagira.
OMS ivuga ko ibihugu bifite ubushobozi bwo gukora ibizamini n'ibikoresho bya leta bidasanzwe by'ikoranabuhanga mu kurwanya COVID-19 bizatuma imibare y'abarwayi ba mbere n'ibisubizo icumi bya mbere by'abanduye COVID-19 bohererezwa umwe mu ma laboratwari 16 yemewe na OMS kugira ngo bagerageze gusuzuma.
Muri ibyo bigo 16 byemewe, 7 biri muri Aziya, 5 muri Afurika, 2 muri Afurika, 1 muri Amerika y'Amajyaruguru, na 1 muri Ositaraliya.
Mu mbonerahamwe ikurikira, urutonde rw'abantu banduye %  rufatwa hakurikijwe gahunda z'igihugu z'imibonano mpuzabitsina.
Ibihugu bizajya byigenzurira abaganga gusa, bizagira umubare munini w'abanduye ugereranyije n'ibihugu bizajya bigenzurira abantu bose, baba bafite ibimenyetso cyangwa badafite.
Gukaraba intoki, nanone bita isuku y'intoki, ni igikorwa cyo gukaraba intoki kugira ngo ziveho ubutaka, amavuta, ubwandu n'ibindi bintu byanduye.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi mu gihe cy'ingenzi ku munsi bifasha kwirinda indwara z'uburwayi, urugero nk'icumu, zituruka mu munyu kandi zikaba zitangwa mu kanwa.
Nanone abantu bashobora kurwara indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, urugero nk'ibicurane cyangwa ibicurane, urugero nko gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, mu mazuru cyangwa mu kanwa (urugero nk'ibicurane).
Amasaha atanu y'ingenzi ku munsi, ni aya mbere na nyuma yo kugura, nyuma yo gusukura imishwaro cyangwa gukukura inkoko, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo guteka cyangwa gukorakora ku nyama itoshye, ifi cyangwa inkoko.
Iyo nta sabuni n'amazi bihari, ushobora gukaraba intoki.
Mbere yo guteka, mu gihe uteka no nyuma yo guteka.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi.
Nyuma yo gukura umwana no kumwambika umwenda cyangwa kumuhanagura.
Nyuma yo gukorakora mu mazuru, gusogongera cyangwa guturika.
Nyuma yo gukora ku nyamaswa, ku biribwa by'inyamaswa cyangwa ku maraso y'inyamaswa.
Kugira isuku mu ntoki mu buvuzi, ni ugusuzuma niba hari ikintu runaka kigomba gukorwa mu gihe cy'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukoresha umuti cyangwa imiti bishobora gutuma indwara idakira cyangwa ngo ikwirakwize.
Impamvu y'ibanze ituma abaganga bakaraba intoki ni ukugira ngo bakureho ubukana bw'ibicurane (mikorobe, virusi cyangwa izindi ndwara ziterwa n'uburwayi) n'ibindi bintu bishobora kutugirira nabi cyangwa kutugirira nabi.
Ni iby'ingenzi cyane ku bantu bakora ibiribwa cyangwa abaganga, ariko nanone ni iby'ingenzi ku bantu bose.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kanini ku buzima, urugero nko kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara z'icyorezo, Coronavirus n'izindi ndwara; kwirinda ibintu bishobora gutera iseseme; no kugabanya indwara zo guhumeka;
no kugabanya umubare w'abana bapfa bavutse mu rugo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki bishobora kugira ingaruka ku mibereho y'abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, iyo umuntu ahinduye imyifatire, urugero nko gukaraba intoki akoresheje isabune, ni bwo gusa abana bapfa bazize indwara zo mu mutwe n'iz'ihindagurika.
Ibyo bintu byoroheje bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abana bapfa bazize iyo ndwara, bigera kuri 50%.
Imyitozo yo gushyigikira isuku y'amaboko ishobora gutuma umuntu arwara ibicurane incuro eshatu, kandi ni ingenzi cyane mu birebana no kugeza amazi meza mu bihugu bikennye.
48% by'indwara z'ibicurane zishobora guterwa no gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni uburyo bworoshye kandi bworoshye bwo kwirinda indwara z'ibicurane n'indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero (ARI), ni umuco w'ingenzi ugomba gukurikizwa mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu duce twose tw'isi.
Indwara y'ubwonko ifite ubukana bukomeye cyane, ari yo ndwara y'ubwonko ihitana abana benshi mu nyanja, ihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 1.8 buri mwaka.
Imyotsi y'amahaha ihitana abana bagera hafi kuri miriyoni 3.5 buri mwaka.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye Ryita ku Buzima (UNICEF) rivuga ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo guhumeka bishobora gukiza abantu benshi kurusha imiti cyangwa inkingo, bikagabanya mu gihembwe kimwe cy'abahitanywe n'indwara z'ubuhumekero n'izindi ndwara zikomeye.
Gukaraba intoki akenshi bifatanyije n'indi gahunda zo gukoresha amazi, isuku no kwita ku buzima (UBUGENZUZI).
Nanone gukaraba intoki bituma umuntu atagira umwanda.
Uburyo bumwe bwo gukaraba intoki ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora kwangiza uruhu rw'umubiri kandi bigatuma ruba runyugunyutse.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2012 muri Danimarike bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki mu buryo burenze urugero bishobora gutuma umuntu akomeza kwifata, akagira indwara y'ibibembe cyangwa y'uruhu rw'amaboko.
Gukaraba intoki birenze urugero ni kimwe mu bimenyetso by'indwara ifata abantu benshi.
Hari ibintu bitanu by'ingenzi umuntu akoresha kugira ngo akomeze kwiyuhagira intoki ze akoresheje isabune: nyuma yo kuva mu kanwa (kwogesha, guhaha), nyuma yo gukaraba umwana (kuvanaho no kwambara umwenda), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya no mbere/nyuma yo guteka cyangwa gukora ku nyama itoshye cyangwa inkoko.
Hari igihe gukaraba intoki neza bigomba kuba ari umuco wo kwirinda indwara, urugero nko mu gihe ukaraba intoki mbere no mu gihe umaze kuvura ikibyimba; mu gihe umaze guturika, ukagwa, ukagira amazuru; umaze gukora ku matungo cyangwa ku matungo; no mu gihe umaze gukora ku matungo.
Mu bihugu byinshi, abantu benshi ntibakoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi ku bijyanye no gukaraba intoki mu bihugu 54 mu 2015 bwagaragaje ko 38,7% by'imiryango ikoresha isabune. Mu 2014 ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko Arabiya Sawudite ifite 97% y'abakoraga ibizamini, Amerika ikaba iri hagati ya 77% na 23% y'abakoraga ibizamini byo gukaraba intoki mu mazi n'isabune. Imirimo myinshi ubu ihinduye imyitwarire y'abana. Gukaraba intoki hamwe mu gihe cy'amasaha y'umunsi ni igitekerezo kimwe mu bihugu bikennye cyo kubishyira mu bikorwa.
Igikorwa cy'ingenzi ku buzima bw'umubiri cyakozwe na Minisiteri y'Uburezi ya Filipine ni urugero rw'ibikorwa byo guteza imbere ubuzima bw'abana no kubara.
Gukura amenyo kabiri mu mwaka, kimwe giherekejwe no gukaraba intoki buri munsi n'isabune, no gukaraba amenyo buri munsi n'imiti y'amenyo, ni bimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi by'iyo gahunda yo mu gihugu.
Abagore bo muri Indoneziya bakoresha uwo muti kandi utuma umera neza.
Iyo umuntu akoresheje isabune cyangwa umuti wo kwisuzumira mu mazi, iyo indwara ikomeje gukira.
Amasabune n'imiti yo kugenzura ubwonko bikoreshwa cyane kugira ngo byongere gukoreshwa neza.
Amazi ni yo yonyine ashobora gutuma uruhu rukora neza, kuko ayo mavuta n'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima byo mu butaka bitagomba guterwa n'amazi.
Ariko kandi, iyo umuntu asukuye amazi ahagije, biramworohera.
Amasabune akomeye ashobora kuba afite ubukana bw'ubwonko bw'abantu bayakoresheje mbere.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku buryo isabune ikoreshwa mu kuvura indwara, bwagaragaje ko nta ndwara ishobora gutera kubera ko isaba uburozi.
Ariko CDC ivuga ko isabune y'amazi idakora ku kintu ifite akamaro kanini mu kwirinda ko indwara zidakwirakwira.
Abantu benshi bavuga ko kuba abantu bafite uburwayi bakoresha isabune irimo imiti ihumanya indwara ari byiza.
Kugeza ubu nta kimenyetso kigaragaza ko abantu bashishikarizwa gukoresha imiti itera ubumara cyangwa imiti itera ubwandu bahisemo kugira ngo bakureho iyi ndwara y'ibyorezo.
Ariko kandi, akenshi amasabune aba arimo umuti wo kwica ubwandu, urugero nka triclosan, ari na yo ifite ubwandu bw'ibinyabuzima byinshi byo ku isi.
Ku bw'ibyo, nubwo imiti ikoreshwa mu kurwanya indwara z'ibyorezo idashyirwa mu m savuni iba irimo imiti ihumanya indwara, hari igihe iba idakomeye nk'uko yafashwe.
Uretse ibintu by'ibanze bikoreshwa mu kurinda umubiri, imiti ikomeye ishobora kuba irimo asidi (asidi acétique, asidi ascorbique, asidi lastique) n'ibindi bifasha mu gutegura pH, asidi benzoïque ihitana ubwonko, n'ibindi bifasha umubiri guhumeka (aloe vera, vitamin, menthol, imiti y'ibiti). Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na kaminuza ya Oregon mu rwego rw'ubuzima bwa rusange bwagaragaje ko isabune yo mu mubiri igira akamaro kanini cyane nk'isabune irimo umuti wo kwangiza amagara witwa triclosan.
Amazi yo gukaraba intoki adafite imbaraga ntazica ubwandu.
Iyo ubwonko bw'umubiri bushyuhe cyane (°C 37), ubwonko bw'umubiri burushaho kwiyongera.
Icyakora, amazi y'umuntu arimo isabune yo mu buryo bw'umwuka, atuma amavuta, ubutaka n'udukoko bitagira ingano birushaho gukoreshwa neza kurusha amazi ashyushye.
Icyakora, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abahanga mu bya siyansi bwagaragaje ko gukoresha amazi y'umuntu nta cyo bitwaye mu ntoki.
Igikoresho cyo gukaraba intoki cyangwa umuti wo kuvura intoki ni umuti wo gukaraba intoki udakoresha amazi.
Mu mpera z'imyaka ya 1990 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, imiti yo gukaraba intoki idakoresha amazi (ita no ku mazi yo gukaraba intoki, imiti yo guhumeka intoki cyangwa imiti yo gukaraba intoki) yatangiye gukoreshwa cyane.
Ubusanzwe, ibyo bicuruzwa bifashishwa alcol isopropyle cyangwa ethanol hamwe n'ikintu kimwe cya Carbomer (polymère ya aside acrylique) muri gel, cyangwa umwotsi nk'igiceri mu mazi, cyangwa umura kugira ngo bikoreshwe neza kandi bikurure imbaraga zo guteka za alcol.
Iyo hongewe umwuka wa peteroyide ya hidrojeni mu mazi, bituma umuti uhoraho wo kwica uturemangingo.
Kwirinda indwara ziterwa n'inzoga, ni kimwe mu birwanya ubwandu bw'indwara z'ubumara, ubwandu bw'ibihaha (MRSA na VRE), igituntu n'izindi virusi (harimo SIDA, herpes, RSV, rhinovirus, ubwandu, icyorezo cy'ibicurane n'indwara y'umutima) n'ibishyimbo.
Igikoresho cyo guhumura intoki gifite 70% ya alcol kigabanya 99,97% (gukuraho log ku 3,5, kikongeraho decibel ku 35) by'ubwandu mu ntoki mu masegonda 30 nyuma yo gukoresha, na 99,99% kugeza ku 99,999% (gukuraho log ku 4 kugeza ku 5) by'ubwandu mu ntoki mu minota 1 nyuma yo gukoresha. Igikoresho cyo guhumura intoki gifite ubushobozi bwo kwica indwara nyinshi ariko nta bwo gifite ubushobozi bwo kwica virusi zimwe na zimwe.
Igikoresho cyo gukaraba intoki kirimo alcol nticyumwa na gato n'umugera witwa norovirus (Norwalk), ubusanzwe ushakira mu ngingo.
Mbere na nyuma y'amaboko yombi n'igice cyawo, hanyuma ukaraba impera z'amaboko mu masegonda 30 kugeza ubwo amazi y'ubwoya cyangwa gel yumutse.
Nanone bisaba ko umuntu yoza intoki, akazihuza n'amaboko yombi. Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika Gishinzwe Kurinda Indwara n'Ibirwanisho cyatangaje ko gukaraba intoki ari byo byiza kuruta gukoresha imiti yo kwiyuhagira intoki, cyane cyane iyo intoki zanduye cyane.
Nubwo amazi yo gukaraba intoki akoreshwa cyane bitewe n'uko ari meza cyane kandi akagira ubushobozi bwo kwica indwara, nta cyo yakoreshwa mu gihe nta sabuni irimo.
Gukoresha imiti yo kwiyuhagira intoki irimo alcol bishobora gutuma uruhu rw'umuntu rwumera neza, keretse iyo byongewemo ibikoresho byo kwiyuhagira intoki.
Iyo umuntu ashyiramo glycerine cyangwa ibindi bintu bituma amaboko asubira inyuma, ashobora gutakaza imbaraga zo gukaraba intoki.
Mu gihe cy'igeragezwa ry'urukingo ku bantu, imiti yo gukaraba intoki ikoreshwa mu guhumeka intoki irimo alcol, yagize ingaruka nke ku ruhu rw'umubiri kandi ituma intoki z'abantu zidakomera cyane nk'uko bimeze ku mavi cyangwa imiti ihumanya indwara.
Akenshi, uruhu rwabo ntirwaragaragaye ko ari rutukura, ko rutareraga imbuto, kandi ko rutarwanya imiti irimo inzoga cyangwa imiti y'ubumara.
Abantu benshi bakundaga gukoresha imiti ituma uruhu rw'umuntu rukora neza, aho gukoresha isabune n'amazi mu gukaraba intoki.
Nubwo ibiyobyabwenge bifasha amaboko, ntibivanaho ibiyobyabwenge mu ntoki, ahubwo bigatuma amazi atemba.
Ku bw'ibyo, imiti yo gukaraba intoki ikoreshwa mu buryo bworoheje ugereranyije n'isabune n'amazi, kuko iyo mikorobe iguma mu ntoki.
Ingufu z'imiti yo kwiyeza intoki idakoraho isukari ziterwa ahanini n'ibishyirwamo n'uburyo ikoreshwa, kandi nta kintu kigaragara kigereranywa n'imiti irimo isukari cyangwa isukari iriho isukari 70.
Mu myaka ya vuba aha, imiti irimo chlorure ya benzalkonium yari ifite ubushobozi bwo kwica indwara, mu buryo butandukanye n'iyo mu bwoko bwa alcol, kuko iyo ifashwe cyane, ishobora kuba ifite ibiyimba byinshi ku ruhu.
Mu duce dukennye, abantu bashobora kugura amasabune bakayasimbuza umukungugu cyangwa ubutaka.
Umukungugu cyangwa ubutaka bishobora kuba bikomeye kurusha amazi ubwabyo, ariko ntibigoye nk'isabune.
Ikindi kintu kibabaje ni uko ubutaka cyangwa umukungugu ufite ubumara bishobora gutuma indwara zikwirakwira mu buryo bwuzuye aho kuzibuza.
Nanone kandi, umukungugu n'isabune bivamo umukungugu, kuko iyo bivanze n'amazi, bivamo umuti wa alkali.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye Ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryita ku mibare y'isabuni, rivuga ko iyo nta sabuni iriho, isaba ko isakwa mu mukungugu cyangwa mu musenyi.
Uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki bwashyizweho n'Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara, ni ubu:
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje amazi ashyushye cyangwa ashyushye.
Bavuga ko iyo umukino ukinwa mu mazi, ushobora kuba ufite ubwandu, kandi ko nta cyo bitwaye.
Jya ukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune nyinshi, hakubiyemo no mu mugongo w'amaboko, mu ntoki no munsi y'amaboko.
Amasabune atuma umubiri ugira indwara, kandi ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko iyo abantu bakoresheje isabune, akenshi bamara igihe kirekire basukura intoki zabo neza, aho kuzikoresha mu mazi.
Jya ushyiraho isabune nibura mu masegonda 20.
Ibyo bituma umubiri usukura ubwandu, kandi gukaraba igihe kirekire bituma ubwandu bushobora kwiyongera.
Jya ukaraba intoki neza ukoresheje amazi asohoka.
Iyo umuntu afashe icyuma cyo mu gikombe, ashobora kongera kwandura indwara mu ntoki.
Gukaraba mu myenda myiza cyangwa kureka bikuma mu muyaga.
Amaboko y'amazi arushaho kwanduza vuba. Ibice bikunze kuba bitakoreshwa neza ni urutoki, ikiganza, ibiganza hagati n'amaboko, n'iburyo bw'amaboko.
Ibikoresho byo guhanagura amagi n'ibikoresho byo guhanagura amagi bishobora kugira ubukana bw'ibinyabuzima.
Akenshi, abantu baterwa inkunga yo gukoresha amavuta yo gusuka kugira ngo amaboko atume atuma atagumaho, kuko ashobora kwangiza uruhu rw'umuntu kandi agatuma arwara.
Amavuta yo gusukura y'igiciro gito ashobora gukoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki aho amazi n'isabune bidahari, urugero nko gusuka amazi mu kintu cyangwa igikombe kiri hejuru kandi gifite imyanda ikwiriye no/cyangwa gukoresha umukungugu mu bihugu bikennye. Iyo amazi ari make (urugero mu mashuri yo mu bihugu bikennye), ntibashobora gukoresha amazi, urugero nk'amabati y'amavuta y'amavuta n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwubatsi bidakenerwa.
Tippy-tap ni uburyo bworoshye bwo gukoresha imishwaro yo hejuru, ikurikizwa ku mugozi, kugira ngo isuke amazi ku maboko no ku m savuni.
Gukaraba intoki ni ingenzi mu buzima, ariko hari abantu benshi batashidikanya ku birebana n'uko bakoresha amazi meza.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko imyenda yo gukaraba intoki ifite akamaro kenshi kurusha imashini zo gukaraba intoki zifite imyenda myinshi.
Mu mwaka wa 2008, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri kaminuza ya Westminster mu mujyi wa Londres, bwashyigikiwe n'ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi mu birebana n'impu z'amaboko (European Tissue Symposium), bwatumye habaho ubushakashatsi bw'uburyo bwo gutandukanya impu z'amaboko, imashini zo gutunganya amaboko n'imashini nshya zo gutunganya amaboko.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki no kuzitukura, umubare w'indwara z'intoki wazamutseho 194% n'amaboko 254%.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki no kuzitukura mu mashini zo gutunganya intoki, umubare w'indwara z'intoki wazamutseho 42% n'intoki 15%.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki no kuzihumeka mu gikoresho cyo gukaraba intoki, umubare w'indwara zo mu ntoki wagabanutseho 76%, ugera kuri 77%, kandi abahanga mu bya siyansi bakoze ibizamini kugira ngo barebe niba abantu bakoreshaga imyenda n'imyenda yo gukaraba intoki, bashoboraga kwandura indwara nyuma yo gukaraba intoki incuro nyinshi.
Imashini yo gutunganya intoki, ikora umuyaga ku muvuduko w'ibirometero bigera kuri 180 ku gisanzwe (650 km/h; 400 mph), yashoboraga kohereza uturemangingo duto mu ntoki mu bice byo hagati y'intoki, kandi igakora ku bandi bantu bari muri izo ntoki ku burebure bwa metero 2.
Gukoresha imashini yo gutunganya intoki, bituma uturemangingo duto duto duto tuva ku kintu cya metero 0.25 uturutse ku mashini.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo TÜV Produkt und Umwelt mu mwaka wa 2005, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku buryo butandukanye bwo gutunganya intoki bwagaragaje ko nibura hari uturemangingo duto duto twanduye.
Hari itandukaniro rikurikira mu mibare y'indwara z'ibicurane mu gihe umuntu amaze gukaraba intoki:
Hariho ibigo byinshi bicuruza imashini zo gukaraba intoki, kandi hari itandukaniro riri hagati y'imashini zo gukaraba intoki n'impuzu zo gukaraba intoki.
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje imyenda yo gukaraba intoki ni ubundi buryo bwo gukaraba intoki mu gihe cy'urugendo mu gihe nta sabuni n'amazi bihari.
Ibyoza intoki bigomba kuba bifite alkaloïde igera kuri 60%.
Nyuma y'aho umuhanga mu binyabuzima w'Umuhongiriya witwa Ignaz Semmelweis abonye ko mu mwaka wa 1846, imiti yo gukaraba intoki yakomeje gukoreshwa cyane mu kwirinda indwara mu bitaro.
Hari imashini nyinshi zituma abaganga bibutsa ko bagomba gukaraba intoki mu gihe bibagiwe.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko iyo bakoresheje imiti, indwara zidakwirakwira cyane.
Kugira ngo umuntu akoreshe imiti yo gukaraba intoki, agomba kumara amasegonda 15 ashyira amazi menshi n'isabune cyangwa amavuta mu ntoki.
Amaboko agomba gukatirwa hamwe, hanyuma agateranyirizwa hamwe n'incuti.
Niba hari ikintu cyanduye munsi y'ikamba, dushobora kugikuraho.
Kugira ngo ubwandu bushobore kuguma mu mazi, ni ngombwa ko amazi abura mu ntoki, maze ukayakura mu cyuma gisanzwe.
Iyo amazi amaze gukama, hagomba gukoreshwa imyenda yo gukama kugira ngo amazi agume mu nzu (kandi niba hari irembo ryo gusohoka rikingurwe).
Ibyo bituma intoki z'umuntu zidakira indwara.
Intego yo gukaraba intoki mu buryo bukwiriye ni ukuvanaho ingeso mbi (菌) no kuzirinda.
Hari ikinyamakuru cyo mu Bwongereza cyavuze ko mu bitaro abantu benshi batajya bakaraba intoki, kandi ko abaganga benshi batakaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku barwayi, bigatuma bagira ubwandu.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki neza n'ibindi birungo byoroheje bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abantu banduye indwara ziterwa n'amaraso ku kigero cya 66%.
