Ibikoresho byo kwirinda COVID-19 mu kazi bikoresha uburyo bwo kwirinda no gukumira icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Uburyo bwiza bwo kwirinda akazi buva ku gace k'akazi n'aho kazi kagenda, ku mimerere y'impanuka, ku cyorezo cy'indwara mu gace utuyemo, no ku cyorezo cy'indwara ya COVID-19.
Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Umutekano muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika (OSHA), ivuga ko akazi gashobora guteza akaga gake cyane ari akazi gashobora gutuma abantu batagira aho bahurira n'abandi, kandi ko gashobora gutuma habaho imihati ikomeye yo kwirinda, urugero nko gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, kurwara indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero no kugira isuku no gusukura ahantu bakorera.
Akazi k'ubutabazi bwo hagati ni akazi gakenera guhura kenshi cyangwa hafi y'abantu uzi cyangwa ushobora kuba ufite COVID-19, ariko gashobora kurwara bitewe n'abantu bahura na bo cyangwa ingendo zo mu bihugu byinshi.
Ibyo ni ko bimeze ku bantu bakorera mu bigo by'amashuri, mu kazi, mu bindi bigo by'abantu benshi.
Mu rwego rwo kwirinda impanuka mu rwego rw'itsinda, uretse ibikorwa rusange byo kwirinda indwara, hakenewe gukoresha umuyoboro w'ubuhumekero ufite amabara akomeye, kwirinda guturika, no kugira ibikoresho byo kwirinda umuntu urwaye COVID-19.
OSHA igenzura abaganga n'abakozi bo mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bw'imiti ko abantu bazi ko bafite COVID-19 bashobora guhura n'umuntu ufite ubukana bw'indwara, kandi ikora ibishoboka byose kugira ngo abahanga mu gukora aerosol cyangwa gukora ku byo akora cyangwa gufata ibipimo by'abantu bafite COVID-19 cyangwa bashobora kuba bafite.
Kwirinda akaga ku bantu bakora imirimo ishobora kuba irimo kwirinda imyanya y'ubuhumekero, no kugira imyambaro myiza yo kwirinda.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora guteza akaga gakomeye mu kazi.
