OMS izasaba gusa ko abaganga bakoresha udupfukamunwa kugira ngo bagire ibizamini.
Ku bantu bahabwa ibipimo by'indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, bakirinda cyangwa bakagenda n'abanduye COVID-19 nta bikorwa bya Aerosol, OMS yemera gukoresha udupfukamunwa tw'abaganga, amakanzu y'umutekano, cyangwa ibikoresho byo kurinda isura, imyenda, n'amatungo.
Mu gihe ukoresha umuti ushyushye, mu gihe ukoresha umuti wo guhumeka, ushobora gukoresha umuti wo guhumeka witwa N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kugira ngo ibikoresho byose bya PPE bitangirwa bidahagije, OMS izemera gukoresha PPE mu buvuzi bwa telefoni, ibibujije abantu guhura n'abandi, urugero nko kugurisha amadirishya, kwemerera abaganga kwinjira mu cyumba cy'umuntu urwaye COVID-19, gukoresha gusa PPE ikenewe mu gikorwa runaka, gukomeza gukoresha ikintu kimwe gifasha guhumeka kitakurwaho mu gihe gifasha abantu benshi kurwara indwara imwe, kwita ku buryo bwiza no gukoresha izindi PPE, no kudashishikariza abantu badafite ibimenyetso gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
