Angiotensin ihindura ingirabuzimafatizo 2 (ACE2) ni ingirabuzimafatizo iri hanze y'ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso, mu ngingo, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu ngingo.
ACE2 ihagarika ingufu za angiotensin mu guhindura ingufu za enzyme (ACE) mu kugabanya ingufu za angiotensin-II no kuzamura ang(1-7) ikayihindura umuti ukoreshwa mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 na yo ikoreshwa mu gutera virusi ya coronavirusi.
Igitekerezo cy'uko umuntu yagira icyo akora ku mubiri we cyitwa hACE2.
Angiotensin encode 2 ni ingirabuzima fatizo ya zinc iri hejuru y'ingirabuzima fatizo z'umubiri.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 irimo peptidase M2 ifite icyiciro cya N n'icya C ifite icyiciro cya C cy'umurava w'umurava.
ACE2 ni ubwoko bw'imiterere y'amaraso y'ibinyabuzima by'umubiri, ikora imirimo yo kwandika ingirabuzimafatizo hanze y'ingirabuzimafatizo n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
Icyiciro cyo mu ngirabuzimafatizo cyo mu mubiri cya ACE2 giherekezwa n'indi ndwara yitwa sheddase, hanyuma igakwirakwira mu maraso, hanyuma igakwirakwira mu maraso.
ACE2 igizwe n'ingingo nyinshi: ACE2 ifatanye n'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso z'urugero rwa II z'ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso z'uruhu, imitsi n'imihimba y'amaraso y'intoki n'imitsi y'amaraso y'ingingo z'umubiri.
Nanone, muri ACE2 harimo uruhu rw'ibinyabuzima, uruhu rw'ibinyabuzima, uruhu rw'ibinyabuzima n'uruhu rw'ubwonko.
ACE2 ni yo ikora imirimo ya mbere.
ACE ifata homoni ya angiotensin I na angiotensin II igahita ihinduka.
ACE2 ifatanye na carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine na angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-pPhe) hanyuma igakorerwa kohydrolyse mu gihumura cy'umuti cyitwa angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora no guhuza na peptide nyinshi nka [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, na ghrelin.
Nanone ACE2 itegura imyenda ya amino acid idasesuye itwara SLC6A19 kandi yari ifite indwara ya Hartnup.
Genzura poroteyine yo mu gikingirizo, ACE2 ni cyo cyorezo cya mbere cy'ingirabuzimafatizo za coronavirusi, hamwe na HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi yatewe na SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi yatewe na COVID-19).
Mu buryo bwumvikana neza, guhuza uruvange rwa poroteyine ya S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 na ACE2 ku ngirabuzimafatizo hejuru y'ingirabuzimafatizo bizatuma indwara y'ingirabuzimafatizo igenda ituma virusi igenda itera hamwe n'imwe mu miryango iri mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Iki kigo cy'inzira kigomba gukora inganda za proteine S na serine protease TMPRSS2, ari nayo irimo kuvumbura uburyo bwo kuvura bushobora gufasha. Ibi byatumye bamwe mu bantu bashobora kwangiza ACE2, mu ngirabuzimafatizo, kugira ngo bagerageze kurwanya ubwandu.
Icyakora, abanyeshuri n'abanyamategeko bo muri ako gace bavuga ko ari ngombwa gukomeza gukurikiza imiti ya ACE n'iyo ARB.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku rwego rw'ikoranabuhanga n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012 bwagaragaje ko "gukoresha ACE" kugabanya ibyago byo kurwara indwara ya nyumonia ku kigero cya 34%.
Ariko kandi, ibyago byo kurwara indwara ya nyumoniya byagabanutse cyane ku bantu bavurwa na ACE, cyane cyane ku barwayi b'umutima.
Gufata imiti ya ACE byongeraga ubukana bw'ubwandu bw'imishwarara, ariko ingaruka zabyo ntizabaga zikomeye cyane ku byo umuntu ashobora kuba afite.
Icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibihaha cyitwa ACE2 (rhACE2) cy'abantu ni uburyo bushya bwo kuvura indwara z'ububabare bw'ibihaha, kandi cyakomeje gutuma ibihaha bikomeza kwiyongera kandi bikagira umwuka mubi mu ngurube, ndetse no mu bagore bafite indwara yo guhumeka nabi.
Ubusanzwe, ubuzima bw'umuntu bw'ikiremwamuntu cya rhACE2 ni amasaha 10 kandi buri gihe kiba gifite iminota 30 cyangwa amasaha 24.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bwagaragaje ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti mwiza ku bantu bafite ingufu nyinshi mu kurwanya ingufu za renin-angiotensin (RAS inhibitors) cyangwa ingufu nyinshi mu gutwara ingufu za angiotensin. rhACE2 yagenzuwe mu buvuzi mu kuvura indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Porogaramu za COVID-19 ni porogaramu za telefoni zigenewe gukurikirana abantu bashobora kuba barwaye icyorezo cya coronavirus cyo mu 2019-20. Reba, uburyo bwo kumenya (people) abantu bashobora kuba bari kumwe n'umuntu wari urwaye.
Hari andi mashyirahamwe menshi y'ubucuruzi yagezeho, ndetse n'ahandi hakoreshejwe leta.
Uburyo bwinshi bwo gukurikirana abantu bwagiye bushyirwaho hakoreshejwe porogaramu za telefoni.
Abantu ntibakunda kureba ibintu by'ibanga by'abantu, ahubwo bagenzura uburyo bwo kumenya aho abantu bari.
Mu bintu by'ibanga abantu batagira icyo bitaho, harimo ibimenyetso bya Bluetooth bifasha umuntu kumenya niba hari telefoni z'abantu.
Ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple batangaje ko bazashyiraho uburyo bwo gushyigikira iyi porogaramu ya Bluetooth muri Android na iOS.
