Porogaramu yashyizweho na Minisiteri y'Itumanaho na Tekinoloji muri Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Ku itariki ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu yari itegereje kwemerwa na Google Play na Apple App Store.
Ku itariki ya 12 Mata, leta yatangaje ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abantu imaze kugera kure, kandi ko izashobora gukoreshwa mu byumweru biri imbere. Porogaramu nk'izo ziri gukorwa muri Irilande, no mu Bufaransa (StopCovid).
Australia na Nouvelle-Zélande bifuza gukoresha porogaramu ikoreshwa muri Singapore TraceTogether na protocol ya BlueTrace. Uburusiya burimo gukora porogaramu izagenzura abantu bafite COVID-19 baba i Moscou, izakorwa mu rwego rwo kubahiriza umutekano wo hanze.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu mu by'ubuhinzi bw'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yavuze ko hari byinshi byashoboka kuri iyi sisitemu ya porogaramu, urugero nko gupima ibyiza by'ibinyabuzima, ndetse no kugabanya ubushobozi bwo gukora neza kubera ko porogaramu ishobora gufasha abaturage bo mu gace gakennye gusa.
